    Card
    This models.Card class represents a playing card.

    This models.piles.CardColumn class represents one of the seven columns of cards in the middle of the table.

    This other.Command class handles the holding of commands that are handled and passed along to the controller in an information holding object.

    This view.CommandLine class represents the view in an MVC pattern.
    Deck
    This models.Deck class represents a physical deck of 52 playing, with each containing a unique combination of rank and suit.

    This models.piles.Foundation class represents one of the four models.piles in Patience Solitaire that are built up from Ace to King by the player.
    GameController
    This controller.GameController represents the controller in an MVC pattern.
    ICommandLine
    The view.ICommandLine class provides a contract that command line handlers for the game Patience Solitaire are expected to implement.
    IController
    The controller.IController class provides a contract that game controllers for the game Patience Solitaire are expected to implement.
    Player
    This models.Player class represents the player, or more specifically the player's hand.
    Program
    This Program class runs the game of Patience Solitaire.

    Table
    This models.Table class represents the physical table space used to hold the components for the game Patience Solitaire.
    WastePile
    This models.piles.WastePile class represents the waste/discard pile of cards used in Patience Solitaire that receives cards from the deck and is refilled into the deck.
